00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:31.800
Nakikiusap ako sa Kamahalan, magpakita ka ng kaunting awa.

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:32.759
City Lord Chen.

00:03:33.520 --> 00:03:34.759
Kung patuloy kang nakikialam,

00:03:35.039 --> 00:03:36.599
